research/history_archive/13_20260326_175854/logs/agent_action_0067.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"`lowrank_soft_codebook_residual` has now established frontier wins at `K=16` and `K=8`; pushing the same fixed recipe to `K=4` may create a new non-dominated ultra-low-K point and potentially beat the current `K=4` anchor from `lowrank_residual`.","summary":"Run one controlled parameter-only experiment at `K=4` with `lowrank_soft_codebook_residual`, keeping `EF=12`, `signum`, `LR=3.2e-3`, and `AUXK_ALPHA=0.0` fixed so `K` is the only changed variable.","change_type":"param_only","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"smaller_k","family_name":"lowrank_soft_codebook_residual","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"This follows the strongest available signal with a single-variable step. The family already improved the frontier at `K=8`, so the next highest-value question is whether that gain extends into the `K=4` slot rather than reopening broader architecture search immediately.","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_soft_codebook_residual"},{"key":"K","value":"4"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"12"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"signum"},{"key":"LR","value":"3.2e-3"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.0"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["Round 67 tests whether `lowrank_soft_codebook_residual`, now on the frontier at `K=16` and `K=8`, can extend into the ultra-low-K regime at `K=4` under the same fixed recipe.","Keep architecture and recipe fixed (`EF=12`, `signum`, `LR=3.2e-3`, `AUXK_ALPHA=0.0`) so `K` is the only changing dimension.","Success criterion is beating the current `K=4` frontier anchor (`lowrank_residual`, FVU `0.1484663188457489`) or at least establishing a clearly competitive lower-K tradeoff for the family."],"next_hypotheses":["If `K=4` wins, test `K=2` with the same family to see how far the low-K extension holds.","If `K=4` is close but slightly behind, consider one confirmatory rerun before concluding the family bottoms out at `K=8`.","If `K=4` clearly loses, keep `lowrank_soft_codebook_residual` as strongest in the `K=8-16` band and resume new-family search for `K<=4`."],"primary_variable":"k"}

